/*		This file contains code for running a demonstration of the		*/
/*		DMA audio inputs and AXI-memory mapped filter program			*/
/*																		*/
/*																		*/
/************************************************************************/
/*  Notes:																*/
/*																		*/
/*		- The DMA max burst size needs to be set to 16 or less			*/
/*																		*/
/************************************************************************/
/*  Revision History:													*/
/* 																		*/
/*		9/6/2016(SamL): Created										    */
